    <div class="span6">
        <h2 >6. Advanced / Offline transaction (optional)</h2>
        <p>What happens if the server goes down?</p>
        <p>You can manually input the other party's invitation code to gain access to the funds without the server.</p>
        <p>After pasting in the invitation code, you can click the "Claim Funds" button the Main tab to calculate the private key</p>
<br />
        <p><b>As long as both buyer and seller backs up their webpage, they will always be able to complete the transaction between themselves by trading their invite codes!</b> </p>
        <br />
    </div>

    

    
</div>